<Br>
<font face=helvetica size=2 color=#000080><b>Quake 3 Depot Update</b> - 08:07:22</font>
<br><br><blockquote>
Got an update from the <a href=http://www.quake3depot.com/>Quake 3 Depot</a><br><br><blockquote>

Just to let you know, we finished the first week here at the Quake3 Depot with the following stats:
Servers: 34, Mods:23, Maps:49, Models:13, Skins:17.  Developers who registered to submit: 88.
The Quake3 Depot is an online search engine dedicated to all things Quake3. Developers can submit their work, images and developer profiles for everyone to see, and gamers can search for servers, mods, levels, models, and skins in a wide variety of ways.<br><br>

We are accepting any and all submissions for servers, mods, maps, models, and skins at <a href=http://www.quake3depot.com/html/submissions.html>http://www.quake3depot.com/html/submissions.html</a></blockquote>


<b><p align=right>Update by <a href="mailto:iamfury@gamedesign.net">Fury</a></p></b>
</blockquote>
<h3>Go <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net">back</a> to the main news page...</h3>
			</font>
